<p>Vancouver residents can take advantage of multiple incentive programs for solar and HVAC installations. The federal solar Investment Tax Credit (ITC) provides a 30% tax credit for solar panel systems installed through 2032, significantly reducing upfront costs. Washington State offers additional incentives including sales tax exemptions on solar equipment and renewable energy production incentives through the Renewable Energy System Cost Recovery Program.</p>

